    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                In <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>onorem</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>omus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ivinae</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Deo Invicto <lb n="2"/>Mytrhe <note>sic</note> ara<lb break="no" n="3"/>m ex voto dei <lb n="4"/>de suo impen<lb break="no" n="5"/>dio <expan><abbr>instituer</abbr><ex>unt</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>A</abbr><ex>ulus</ex></expan> Gratius Iuven<lb break="no" n="7"/>is pater sacroru<lb break="no" n="8"/>m et <expan><abbr>A</abbr><ex>ulus</ex></expan> Gratius Po<lb break="no" n="9"/>tens <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>iles</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>egionis</ex></expan> XXII mat<lb break="no" n="10"/>rica<supplied reason="lost">ri</supplied>us fratres <lb n="11"/>dedic<supplied reason="lost">aver</supplied>unt co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ule</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Afri</abbr><ex>cano</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Z. 1 befindet sich auf der corona. Reste von roter Farbe in den Buchstaben. Z. 1 befindet sich auf der corona. Z. 4: Text hinter M nachträglich korrigiert aus ET TEMPLVM. Z. 7: IVVEN nachträglich aus IOVEN korrigiert. (B): Behrens, MZ: Z. 10/11: mat/ricar[ius]; CIMRM: Z. 10/11: ma/tricarius; Behrens, MZ: Z. 12: dedic[averun]t; CIMRM: Z. 12: dedic(aver)unt.</p>
            </div>
